title: Homelab

content:
Hello, my name is Ian. I have 5 years experience working in the field of technology. I am currently an IT Knowledge Management Specialist with The Anschutz Corporation in Denver. I am additionally a current Computer Science student at CU Boulder. In my spare time I enjoy tinkering in my homelab, gardening, snowboarding, hiking and backpacking with my Wife, and of course reading.
I have always been passionate about technology and hope that you enjoy my website while you’re here.
